Package: InterCellar
Title: InterCellar: an R-Shiny app for interactive analysis of cell-cell
  interactions
Version: 0.99.0
Authors@R: person('Marta', 'Interlandi', email = 'marta.interlandi01@gmail.com', role = c('cre', 'aut'))
Description: InterCellar is implemented as an R/Bioconductor Package
  containing a Shiny app that allows users to interactively analyze the results
  of cell-cell interactions for scRNA-seq data.
